y, ‘light in colouring’)."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Blanche d'Acheux-en-Amiénois was born about 1205, in France, her father, Hector d'Acheux-en-Amiénois, was 24 and her mother, Jacqueline de Sarton, was 15. She had at least 4 sons with Aubert Ier “le Chien” de Longueval. She died about 1284, at the age of 81."},"et":{"environ 1205–environ 1284":"umbes 1205–umbes 1284","1205–1284":"1205–1284","1190–1262":"1190–1262","1225–1273":"1225–1273","1235–Male":"1235–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1182–1239":"1182–1239","1191–1254":"1191–8.jaanuar1254kuni7.jaanuar1255","1190":"1190","environ 1235":"umbes 1235","environ 1284":"umbes 1284","1262":"1262","1273":"1273","1284":"1284","1182":"1182","1191":"1191","1239":"1239","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","1235":"1235","1254":"8. jaanuar 1254 kuni 7. jaanuar 1255","environ 1239":"umbes 1239","environ 1205":"umbes 1205","Sieur, de Longueval, Ch‚telain, de PÈronne":"Péronne, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa","Acheux-en-Amiénois, France":"Acheux-en-Amiénois, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"environ 1205–environ 1284":"noin 1205–noin 1284","1205–1284":"1205–1284","1190–1262":"1190–1262","1225–1273":"1225–1273","1235–Male":"1235–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1182–1239":"1182–1239","1191–1254":"1191–vuodesta8.tammikuuta1254vuoteen7.tammikuuta1255","1190":"1190","environ 1235":"noin 1235","environ 1284":"noin 1284","1262":"1262","1273":"1273","1284":"1284","1182":"1182","1191":"1191","1239":"1239","1205":"1205","1225":"1225","1235":"1235","1254":"vuodesta 8. tammikuuta 1254 vuoteen 7. tammikuuta 1255","environ 1239":"noin 1239","environ 1205":"noin 1205","Sieur, de Longueval, Ch‚telain, de PÈronne":"Péronne, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Ranska","France":"Ranska","Acheux-en-Amiénois, France":"Acheux-en-Amiénois, Somme, Picardie, Ranska"},"fr":{"environ 1205–environ 1284":"environ 1205–environ 1284","1205–1284":"1205–1284","1190–1262":"1190–1262","1225–1273":"1225–1273","1235–Male":"1235–Décédé","–Male":"Décédé",